Token.Abstract: An ordering can determine the relative ordering of any two objects in a domain.
Compares the two given arguments according to this ordering.

Parameter.Name: arg1
Parameter.Abstract: The first argument to be compared

Parameter.Name: arg2
Parameter.Abstract: The second argument to be compared

ReturnValue.Abstract: Either {@link #FIRSTLESSTHANSECOND}, {@link #FIRSTEQUALTOSECOND} or {@link #FIRSTGREATERTHAN_SECOND}, depending on whether the first argument is less than, equal to, or greater than the second argument in this ordering
